<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Malaehi... My Sun-runner... I have done you wrongly, and for this I will not ask forgiveness.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
Malaehi opened her mouth to speak, but Nathomin shook his head to silence her. He had to say everything before he lost courage.<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Malaehi... My Sun-runner... I cannot marry you.. for so many reasons we both know.. And you have so much to learn about passion and so much to teach about love. I cannot promise that I will be there for all of it. but I ... Malaehi .. I wish to be with you, to help you...<br>
