Malaehi.. Ssus'zhar.. I want to walk by your side... Please tell me I can walk with you.. </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot; Nathomin's voice dropped as he whispered. But Malaehi's delecate ears heard well enough, and the words took her breath away...<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Malaehi... I love you.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;<br>
<br>
Malaehi looked into Nathomin's eyes seeking any sign of deception, any trace of Tier'Dal lies.. but there were none.<br>
