<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Innoruuk.....</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot; Nathomin whispered in dread... &quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>No... No innoruuk...Let me go!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot; <br>
<br>
Nathomin's mind screamed out against the pull, cried out against the injustice... cried out for his love... Malaehi.<br>
