<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Why... Why would you prevent me from being with her?</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;  Nathomin knew in that instant that his heart.... that which he had thought Innoruuk's gift/curse was not innoruuk's makeing at all.... That his ability to know hate AND passion... were not innoruuk's gift... but something he had had always... something that was Nathomin's... Innoruuk had lied to him.. <br>
<br>
Nathomin's eyes found focus and they found Malaehi and the Druidess both.. but his eyes were filled with anger.  He turned away from them so that they would not see how he hated...<br>
A scream built up within him... one born of fury and indignation, built of them but powered by his love for Malaehi..<br>
