&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>INNORUUK!!!!... YOU SHRIVELED SEEDLESS ARSE!!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;  <br>
Nathomin breathed deeply as Malaehi stood shocked behind him, reaching out to still him... But he would not forgive this. Could not...<br>
<br>
&quot;<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>I swore an oath Innoruuk. I swore that I would leave the realms of the gods to themselves.... But the Deal is OFF INNORUUK.... I will come to your very house and I will watch it burn... You have tried to take from me... My one joy... It will not happen again You vile gutless pile of Dung!</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->&quot;<br>
